  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:402px;\">\n<div style=\"position: relative; border: 1px solid lightgray\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:The_Reach.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"The Reach and the location of Sunhouse\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Sunhouse\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/400px-The_Reach.png\" width=\"400\" height=\"513\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/600px-The_Reach.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/89/The_Reach.png/800px-The_Reach.png 2x\" /></a><div style=\"position: absolute; z-index: 2; top: 88.9%; left: 28.1%; height: 0; width: 0; margin: 0; padding: 0;\"><div style=\"position: relative; text-align: center; left: -5px; top: -5px; width: 10px; font-size: 10px;\"><img alt=\"The Reach and the location of Sunhouse\" src=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/10px-Red_pog.png\" title=\"Sunhouse\" width=\"10\" height=\"10\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/15px-Red_pog.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/b/b4/Red_pog.png/20px-Red_pog.png 2x\" /></div><div style=\"font-size: 90%; line-height: 110%; z-index:90; position: relative; top: -1.5em; width: 6em; left: -6.5em; text-align: right;\"><span style=\"padding: 1px;\"><b>Sunhouse</b></span></div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumbcaption\"><a href=\"/index.php/The_Reach\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Reach\">The Reach</a> and the location of Sunhouse\n</div>\n</div>\n</div><table>\n\n<tbody><tr><td></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Sunhouse</b>, also called <b>Sunflower Hall</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is the seat of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Cuy\" title=\"House Cuy\">House Cuy</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/The_Reach\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"The Reach\">the Reach</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_sunhouse.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_sunhouse.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> The castle is located on the southern coast of the Reach, east of the <a href=\"/index.php/Redwyne_Straits\" title=\"Redwyne Straits\">Redwyne Straits</a> and southeast of <a href=\"/index.php/Oldtown\" title=\"Oldtown\">Oldtown</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup> The town of <a href=\"/index.php/Cuy\" title=\"Cuy\">Cuy</a> is located outside of Sunhouse's walls.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rawoiaf_sunhouse.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rawoiaf_sunhouse.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Sunhouse&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">It is called <b>Sunflower Hall</b> in <i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-Appendix\" title=\"A Feast for Crows-Appendix\">Appendix</a>, and <a class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.westeros.org/Citadel/Heraldry/Houses/7/\">Westeros.org: Houses in the Reach</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rawoiaf_sunhouse.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_sunhouse.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">2.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rawoiaf_sunhouse.7B